es with a LEGITMATE claim to use this belt.  Anyone who disagrees, doesn't know their ass from their elbow.<br><br>(On a related note, if this belt or anything like it is merited on a raid, anyone selling merit loot before they have anything "better" should be deguilded immediately and blackballed)<br>&nbsp;<br> </td></tr>
